{"tid":1119821,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[日劇]集團左遷","createTime":"2019-04-22T07:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T19:40:22.000Z","uid":4618,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b776bd43c5d135e2bf8bdaa6ab6d2d05de25fdc","tid":1119821,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:58:16.000Z","msg":"睇完第一集<br />\n雖然又係銀行公式嘢，前面悶悶地<br />\n但後面有d感受，個格局好易代入香港<br />\n<br />\n總部(橫山)=硬推中港融合<br />\n大和田=焦土撚，崩壞之後先諗出路<br />\n神木=挽救人情、徒勞無功既年輕一代<br />\n<br />\n福山就係真正上一代獅子山精神面對今日政治困局既態度同迷茫<br />\n我始終想一直做銀行員<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">香港人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9132fa6c657cb4656153441101a2e39dd96fd8e","tid":1119821,"uid":232395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"好想行長同蒲田打得贏呢場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d746aa8161caa9acb1ebef7ac8f41178e86b5d","tid":1119821,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9132fa6c657cb4656153441101a2e39dd96fd8e","tid":1119821,"uid":232395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"好想行長同蒲田打得贏呢場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"講明下克上 贏係100%的波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8a2f556747f0dc5c561ae6301c0a6e21078feb","tid":1119821,"uid":202267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:57:51.000Z","msg":"未睇但有我男人所以準備睇<br />\nLM"},{"pid":"a34ffe8ceb5b4326b3615bfbb6ed2dfbce32c749","tid":1119821,"uid":66839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"睇吉高好過啦"},{"pid":"e9326d349f49e2e86c459d1d01b41481a55031c1","tid":1119821,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a34ffe8ceb5b4326b3615bfbb6ed2dfbce32c749","tid":1119821,"uid":6683